Two security guards were on Saturday night killed in an attack on a mall in Eastleigh, Nairobi. Two others are still missing after the attack at Moyale Mall. Read: Night guard brutally killed in Katoloni Market The gang broke into nine shops and stole property including electronic goods valued at millions of shillings."We were informed of the incident long after it had happened and after the gang had escaped with the goods, it seems they were only interested in the goods from the shops," a police officer said. The bodies of the two guards have taken to the city mortuary.